<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<section class="page-heading">
  <p class="eyebrow">Project Details</p>
  <h1>FarmDirect - Online Marketplace for Farmers</h1>
  <p>Farmers sell agricultural products directly to customers through a simple digital marketplace.</p>
</section>

<section class="section project-grid">
  <article class="feature-card">
    <span>Problem</span>
    <h2>Fair market access</h2>
    <p>Many farmers depend on middlemen, lose profit share, and struggle to reach larger customer markets.</p>
  </article>
  <article class="feature-card">
    <span>Objective</span>
    <h2>Direct connection</h2>
    <p>Farmers list fruits, vegetables, organic products, and grains. Customers browse and buy fresh products directly.</p>
  </article>
  <article class="feature-card">
    <span>Benefit</span>
    <h2>Digital agriculture</h2>
    <p>Farmers receive better prices, customers get fresher products, and small farmers reach a wider market.</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="section architecture">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">System Architecture</p>
    <h2>Three-layer structure</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline">
    <article>
      <strong>Presentation Layer</strong>
      <p>EJS, HTML, CSS, and browser JavaScript provide the user interface.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <strong>Logic Layer</strong>
      <p>Express routes handle authentication, product listing, filtering, and orders.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <strong>Data Layer</strong>
      <p>MongoDB stores users, profile images, product listings, and customer orders.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section split-section">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592982537447-7440770cbfc9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
    alt="Fresh vegetables at a farm market"
  >
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Future Improvements</p>
    <h2>Next steps</h2>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li>Mobile application for farmers and customers.</li>
      <li>Online payment integration.</li>
      <li>Real-time inventory management.</li>
      <li>AI based crop price prediction.</li>
      <li>Delivery tracking system.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

